20doubt%2C%20Palantir%20is%20a%20strong%20hiring%20signal%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20golden%20ticket%20in%20tech%20is%20outdated%2C%26quot%3B%20Fisher%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20real%20hiring%20market%20doesn't%20reward%20brand%20names%20alone%2C%20it%20rewards%20execution%20and%20adaptability%20%E2%80%94%20who%20built%20what%20and%20scaled%20systems%20at%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisher%20said%20that%20tech%20companies%20often%20seek%20to%20hire%20from%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20high-caliber%26quot%3B%20talent%20pools%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Framp-card%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERamp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Stripe%2C%20Linear%2C%20and%20Notion%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20aren't%20clients%20of%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESines%20said%20that%20Palantir%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20seeking%20out%20top%20talent%20and%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Brigorous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bresults-oriented%26quot%3B%20hiring%20strategy.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20that%20while%20it%20carries%20a%20%26quot%3Bbadge%20of%20honor%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20some%20clients%2C%20it%20may%20signal%20too%20much%20intensity%20for%20others.%20It%20depends%20on%20how%20companies%20perceive%20culture%2C%20Sines%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarah%20Sharghi%2C%20a%20job%20search%20coach%20and%20former%20recruiter%20at%20tech%20companies%20including%20Google%2C%20Lyft%2C%20Uber%2C%20and%20TikTok%2C%20said%20that%20while%20Palantir's%20hiring%20process%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20stringent%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20good%20employee%20at%20Palantir%20may%20not%20be%20a%20good%20employee%20everywhere%20else%20because%20%26quot%3Bthere%20might%20be%20some%20nuances%20to%20some%20companies%20versus%20others%20in%20terms%20of%20cultural%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Palantir%20engineer%20who's%20used%20to%20working%20on%20some%20particular%20type%20of%20technology%20might%20not%20thrive%20in%20another