erations%20at%20the%20partially%20collapsed%20Telangana's%20Srisailam%20Left%20Bank%20Canal%20tunnel%20entered%20the%20sixth%20day%20on%20Thursday.%20Eight%20workers%20have%20been%20trapped%20in%20the%20tunnel%20since%20February%2022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fslbc-srisailam-left-bank-tunnel-telangana-tunnel-collapse-6-days-and-counting-teams-intensify-rescue-efforts-at-collapsed-telangana-tunnel-7805965%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20India%20Request%2C%20US%20Grants%20Visa%20Interview%20For%20Injured%20Student's%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEarlier%20today%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry's%20Americas%20Division%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20US%20government.%20Sources%20said%20travel%20permits%20for%20medical%20emergencies%20are%20normally%20given%20quickly%20and%20it%20is%20unclear%20what%20led%20to%20the%20delay%20in%20this%20instance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Shinde%20-%20a%20student%20at%20California%20State%20University%20-%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%2C%20including%20fractures%2C%20after%20she%20was%20mowed%20down%20from%20behind%20by%20a%20four-wheeler%20on%20February%2014.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHer%20family%20applied%20for%20a%20visa%2048%20hours%20later%2C%20but%20the%20application%20has%20been%20pending%20since.%20Ms%20Shinde's%20uncle%2C%20Kadam%20Shinde%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffamily-of-comatose-indian-student-nilam-shinde-in-us-getting-visa-slot-for-2026-7806173%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearliest%20available%20date%20is%20for%20next%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Shinde's%20family%20said%20the%20crash%20left%20her%20with%20fractures%20in%20both%20arms%20and%20both%20legs%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finjures-on-hea