ndi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffilmmaker-ashutosh-gowarikers-son-konark-is-set-to-tie-the-knot-with-niyati-kanakia-on-march-2%2Farticleshow%2F118599985.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSuch%20People%20Should%20Be%20Hanged%26quot%3B%3A%20Eknath%20Shinde%20On%20Pune%20Bus%20Rapist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReacting%20strongly%20to%20the%20rape%20of%20a%2027-year-old%20woman%20in%20a%20bus%20in%20Pune%2C%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20said%20that%20no%20one%20will%20be%20spared%20and%20people%20who%20commit%20such%20crimes%20should%20be%20hanged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20a%20domestic%20help%2C%20was%20raped%20at%20the%20busy%20Swargate%20Bus%20Stand%20-%20which%20is%20just%20100%20metres%20from%20a%20police%20station%20-%20between%205.45%20and%206%20am%20on%20Tuesday.%20Police%20have%20said%20the%20suspect%20is%2036-year-old%20Dattatraya%20Ramdas%20Gade%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20theft%2C%20robbery%20and%20chain-snatching%20incidents%20in%20the%20past%20and%20has%20been%20out%20on%20bail%20since%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20rape%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pune%20incident%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20Whoever%20the%20accused%20is%2C%20no%20matter%20which%20party%20he%20belongs%20to%2C%20he%20will%20not%20be%20spared.%20Such%20people%20should%20be%20hanged.%20The%20damaged%20bus%20in%20the%20depot%20should%20be%20auctioned%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20has%20been%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20opposition%20over%20the%20rape%20in%20one%20of%20the%20state's%20biggest%20cities%2C%20which%20is%20also%20an%20education%20and%20information%20technology%20hub.%20Members%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20faction%20staged%20a%20protest%20outside%20the%20Swargate%20police%20station%20on%20Thursday%20and%20the%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20of%20putting%20more%20emphasis%20on%20freebies%20for%20women%20than%20ensuring%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Nirbhaya%20gangrape%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Delhi%2C%20people%20changed%20the%20regime.%20You%20(BJP-led%20Maharashtra%20government)%20promote%20'Laadki%20Bahin'%20scheme%20for%20women%2C%20but%20ignore%20basic%20issues%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20President%20Harshwardhan%20Sapkal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20assured%20that%20strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20and%20Mr%20Shinde's%20fellow%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%20said%20the%20police%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused%20immediately.%20Mr%20Pawar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20also%20stressed%20that%20the%20only%20punishment%20for%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20can%20be%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20of%20rape%20at%20the%20Swargate%20bus%20station%20is%20extremely%20unfortunate%2C%20painful%2C%20infuriating%20and%20shameful%20to%20all%20in%20civilised%20society.%20The%20crime%20committed%20by%20the%20accused%20is%20unforgivable%20and%20there%20can%20be%20no%20other%20punishment%20for%20him%20than%20death.%20I%20have%20directed%20the%20Pune%20police%20commissioner%20to%20personally%20look%20into%20this%20matter%20and%20investigate%20it%20and%20arrest%20the%20accused%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransport%20Minister%20Pratap%20Sarnaik%20has%20also%20announced%20a%20security%20audit%20for%20all%20bus%20depots%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20guards%20at%20the%20Swargate%20bus%20depot%20have%20been%20replaced%20and%20a%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20to%20quickly%20sell%20off%20the%20buses%20that%20are%20out%20of%20service%20at%20the%20depots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELights%20Of%20Bus%20Were%20Off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20woman%20was%20waiting%20to%20board%20a%20bus%20to%20her%20hometown%20in%20Satara%20district%20when%20she%20was%20approached%20by%20Gade.%20The%20man%20told%20her%20that%20a%20bus%20parked%20in%20a%20corner%20of%20the%20depot%20would%20take%20her%20to%20her%20destination%20and%20when%20she%20hesitated%20because%20its%20lights%20were%20off%2C%20told%20her%20that%20the%20passengers%20inside%20were%20sleeping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20locked%20the%20door%20of%20the%20bus%20and%20raped%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pune%20police%20have%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-bus-rape-case-suspect-name-dattatraya-ramdas-gade-photo-released-cops-announce-rs-1-lakh-reward-7805085%5C%22%3Ea%20reward%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20Gade's%20arrests%20and%20have%20also%20released%20a%20photo.%20The%20Crime%20Branch%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-bus-rape-accused-dattatraya-ramdas-gade-found-hiding-in-sugarcane-field-cops-use-drones-7806545%5C%22%3Etrack%20him%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2013%20teams%20have%20been%20formed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740648060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fs9ji0ekg_pune-bus-stand-_625x300_26_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsuch-people-should-be-hanged-eknath-shinde-on-pune-bus-rapist-7806454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reacting%20strongly%20to%20the%20rape%20of%20a%2027-year-old%20woman%20in%20a%20bus%20in%20Pune%2C%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20said%20that%20no%20one%20will%20be%20spared%20and%20people%20who%20carry%20out%20such%20crimes%20should%20be%20hanged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsuch-people-should-be-hanged-eknath-shinde-on-pune-bus-rapist-7806454%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Legendary%20Actor%20Gene%20Hackman%2C%20Wife%20And%20Dog%20Found%20Dead%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo-time%20Oscar%20winner%20Gene%20Hackman%20and%20his%20wife%20Betsy%20Arakawa%20have%20been%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20home%20in%20Santa%20Fe%2C%20New%20Mexico%2C%20US.%20The%20couple%20reportedly%20died%20along%20with%20their%20dog.%20Mr%20Hackman%20was%2095%20and%20his%20wife%2063.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanta%20Fe%20County%20Sheriff%20Adan%20Mendoza%20confirmed%20the%20death%20and%20said%20the%20case%20is%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20confirm%20that%20both%20Gene%20Hackman%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20found%20dead%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20at%20their%20residence%20on%20Sunset%20Trail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20active%20investigation%20-%20however%2C%20at%20this%20time%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20foul%20play%20was%20a%20factor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mendoza%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcewkkkvkzn9o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mendoza%20didn't%20provide%20clarity%20on%20the%20cause%20or%20time%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20we're%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20preliminary%20death%20investigation%2C%20waiting%20on%20approval%20of%20a%20search%20warrant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201930%2C%20Mr%20Hackman%20played%20over%20100%20roles.%20He%20won%20two%20Oscars%20-%20best%20actor%20for%20his%20role%20as%20Jimmy%20%26quot%3BPopeye%26quot%3B%20Doyle%20in%20The%20French%20Connection%2C%20and%20best%20supporting%20actor%20for%20playing%20Little%20Bill%20Daggett%20in%20Unforgiven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740648000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fvllo06t_gene-hackman_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flegendary-actor-gene-hackman-wife-and-dog-found-dead-at-home-7806695%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gene%20Hackman%20and%20his%20wife%20Betsy%20Arakawa%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20US%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flegendary-actor-gene-hackman-wife-and-dog-found-dead-at-home-7806695%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Look%20Beyond%20Russia-Ukraine%20Or%20Gaza%2C%20'Smaller'%20Wars%20Are%20Reshaping%20The%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20glance%20at%20recent%20history%20is%20always%20insightful%20in%20the%20study%20of%20geopolitics%20and%20geosecurity.%20Let's%20rewind%20to%201990%E2%80%94a%20pivotal%20year%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20just%20returned%20with%20the%20last%20elements%20of%20the%20Indian%20Peacekeeping%20Force%20(IPKF)%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20was%20headed%20to%20an%20Army%20cantonment%20in%20a%20'peace'%20location.%20However%2C%20our%20plans%20quickly%20changed%20when%20we%20were%20diverted%20to%20Punjab.%20We%20were%20to%20form%20the%20frontline%20of%20forces%20crossing%20the%20River%20Sutlej%20to%20counter%20Pakistan's%20intransigence%E2%80%94its%20launch%20of%20Exercise%20Zarb-e-Momin%20and%20its%20sponsorship%20of%20militancy%20and%20terror%20in%20Punjab.%20Zarb-e-Momin%2C%20a%20military%20training%20manoeuvre%20with%20operational%20intent%2C%20was%20designed%20to%20send%20a%20message%20and%20divert%20our%20attention.%20Meanwhile%2C%20conflict%20was%20also%20brewing%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20broader%20geopolitical%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Story%20Of%20Al%20Qaeda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%20The%20Berlin%20Wall%20had%20just%20fallen%2C%20and%20the%20Soviets%20were%20still%20withdrawing%20from%20Afghanistan.%20Punjab%20was%20in%20turmoil%2C%20diverting%20strategic%20attention%20in%20multiple%20directions.%20The%20Iran-Iraq%20War%20had%20ended%20just%20a%20few%20years%20earlier.%20Victorious%20jihadis%20from%20across%20the%20Islamic%20world%20were%20emerging%20from%20the%20rubble%20of%20Afghanistan%20in%201990.%20This%20description%20covers%20only%20a%20small%20section%20of%20the%20world%20then.%20It%20does%20not%20even%20touch%20on%20Africa%2C%20which%20was%20also%20emerging%20from%20the%20shadows%20of%20old%20conflicts%20in%20Somalia%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Namibia%2C%20Angola%2C%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaving%20everything%20else%20aside%2C%20I%20often%20ask%20myself%3A%20where%20did%20Al%20Qaeda%20come%20from%3F%20The%20answer%20traces%20back%20to%20the%20Soviet%20invasion%20of%20Afghanistan%20in%201979%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20global%20call%20for%20jihad%20against%20the%20Soviets.%20The%20US%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20and%20Pakistan%20supported%20the%20Afghan%20mujahideen%20with%20funding%2C%20weapons%2C%20and%20training%20to%20counter%20Soviet%20influence.%20Osama%20bin%20Laden%2C%20a%20wealthy%20Saudi%2C%20joined%20the%20war%20effort%2C%20organising%20foreign%20fighters%20and%20logistical%20support.%20This%20network%20later%20evolved%20into%20Al%20Qaeda%2C%20founded%20in%201988.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Soviets%20withdrew%20in%201989%2C%20bin%20Laden%20and%20other%20jihadists%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20victory%20for%20Islam%20over%20a%20superpower.%20As%20the%20Cold%20War%20ended%20in%201991%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20disengaged%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20leaving%20a%20power%20vacuum.%20Many%20foreign%20jihadists%2C%20including%20bin%20Laden%2C%20believed%20their%20next%20mission%20was%20to%20fight%20Western%20influence%E2%80%94particularly%20the%20US%2C%20which%20they%20saw%20as%20the%20next%20%E2%80%9Coccupying%20power%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Al%20Qaeda%20Became%20a%20Global%20Jihadi%20Network%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Iraq%20invaded%20Kuwait%20in%201990%2C%20bin%20Laden%20offered%20his%20mujahideen%20to%20defend%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20but%20the%20Saudi%20government%20rejected%20him%2C%20inviting%20US%20forces%20instead.%20This%20marked%20his%20formal%20break%20with%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20transforming%20Al%20Qaeda%20from%20an%20anti-Soviet%20group%20into%20a%20global%20jihadist%20movement.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAl%20Qaeda's%20rise%20was%20deeply%20tied%20to%20the%20Cold%20War's%20conclusion.%20The%20Soviet-Afghan%20War%20provided%20the%20military%20experience%2C%20networks%2C%20and%20ideology%20that%20fuelled%20its%20creation.%20After%20defeating%20the%20Soviets%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20abandoned%20Afghanistan%2C%20allowing%20extremism%20to%20fester.%20Bin%20Laden%20and%20his%20followers%20redirected%20their%20jihad%20against%20the%20West%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20global%20terrorist%20threats%20we%20face%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20this%2C%20several%20lessons%20follow.%20First%2C%20whenever%20the%20world%20emerges%20from%20a%20period%20of%20intense%20activity%20and%20lowers%20its%20guard%2C%20it%20is%20often%20struck%20by%20unconventional%20turbulence.%20This%20happened%20in%201989-90%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20terrorism%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20just%20as%20it%20did%20with%20the%20civil%20wars%20in%20Africa%20between%201990%20and%201995.%20The%20movements%20in%20Chechnya%20and%20Bosnia%20were%20also%20linked%20to%20the%20events%20of%20this%20period.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20US%20and%20Coalition%20troops%20from%20Iraq%20in%202011%20ultimately%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20rise%20of%20ISIS%20(Daesh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20ISIS%20suffered%20military%20defeats%20in%20Mosul%20and%20Baghuz%2C%20it%20was%20only%20partially%20displaced%2C%20finding%20refuge%20in%20Afghanistan's%20northern%20badlands.%20Al%20Qaeda%20maintained%20a%20presence%20there%2C%20alongside%20Central%20Asian%20and%20Pakistani%20terrorist%20groups.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Taliban%20remains%20reclusive%20and%20untrustworthy.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRemnants%20of%20ISIS%20also%20persist%20in%20Kurdish-held%20areas%20along%20the%20Syria-Turkey%20border%2C%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20its%20resurgence%20remains%20real.%20If%20northern%20Syria%20and%20the%20Turkish%20border%20region%20remain%20unstable%2C%20ISIS%20could%20exploit%20these%20conditions%20to%20rebuild%20its%20networks%20and%20launch%20new%20offensives.%20The%20combination%20of%20weak%20governance%2C%20regional%20infighting%2C%20and%20existing%20ISIS%20sleeper%20cells%20makes%20this%20an%20ongoing%20and%20serious%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20does%20this%20lead%3F%20In%20the%20first%20month%20of%20the%20new%20US%20President's%20tenure%2C%20the%20world%20order%20is%20already%20facing%20serious%20disruption.%20As%20global%20attention%20is%20drawn%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20trade%20disputes%2C%20and%20tariffs%2C%20seemingly%20small%20issues%20continue%20to%20develop%2C%20often%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20spiral%20into%20major%20crises.%20Remember%20how%20ISIS%20emerged%20in%20June%202014%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20consider%20the%20long-term%20consequences%20of%20the%20mass%20destruction%20in%20Gaza.%20An%20entire%20generation%20of%20Palestinian%20youth%20now%20lives%20without%20hope%E2%80%94a%20sentiment%20that%20extends%20beyond%20the%20youth%20to%20the%20entire%20population.%20For%20those%20who%20have%20endured%20such%20loss%20and%20suffering%2C%20revenge%20and%20retribution%20become%20powerful%20emotions%2C%20and%20the%20blame%20is%20often%20placed%20on%20the%20entire%20world.%20This%20creates%20fertile%20ground%20for%20terror%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wonder%20how%20these%20groups%20sustain%20themselves%E2%80%94with%20resources%2C%20fighters%2C%20and%20finances%E2%80%94we%20have%20seen%20repeatedly%20that%20these%20are%20no%20longer%20significant%20obstacles.%20Ideologies%20are%20abundant%2C%20and%20a%20cause%20(whether%20perceived%20as%20just%20or%20unjust)%20is%20never%20difficult%20to%20manufacture%20when%20retribution%20is%20the%20driving%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Will%20Current%20Gaza%20Turmoil%20Manifest%20Itself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20formal%20or%20direct%20linkage%20between%20Palestinian%20groups%20and%20ISIS.%20The%20latter%20follows%20an%20extreme%20Salafi-jihadist%20ideology%20and%20has%20often%20criticised%20Palestinian%20factions%2C%20including%20Hamas%2C%20for%20being%20too%20nationalistic%20and%20failing%20to%20embrace%20its%20vision%20of%20global%20jihad.%20However%2C%20under%20a%20desperate%20bid%20for%20survival%2C%20Hamas%20could%20change%20its%20stance%2C%20potentially%20opening%20the%20door%20to%20some%20level%20of%20cooperation%20with%20ISIS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20a%20Shia%20organisation%20with%20direct%20allegiance%20to%20Iran%2C%20remains%20a%20priority%20for%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC).%20While%20Hezbollah%20and%20Hamas%20have%20historically%20aligned%20on%20certain%20fronts%2C%20Hamas's%20ideology%20is%20not%20far%20removed%20from%20ISIS-style%20radicalism%2C%20with%20its%20influence%20and%20objectives%20potentially%20spreading%20beyond%20Palestine%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20Arab%20world.%20That%20is%20a%20concern%2C%20particularly%20for%20regional%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%205%2C%202025%2C%20during%20the%20Kashmir%20Solidarity%20Day%20event%20in%20Rawalakot%2C%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%2C%20Hamas%20representatives%E2%80%94Khalid%20Qaddoumi%20and%20Naji%20Zaheer%E2%80%94were%20present.%20They%20received%20notable%20attention%20from%20members%20of%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20and%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20(JeM)%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20Hamas%20officials%20participating%20in%20an%20event%20in%20PoK.%20While%20this%20may%20not%20yet%20signify%20a%20formal%20alliance%2C%20it%20indicates%20a%20growing%20effort%20to%20establish%20wider%20networks%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20transnational%20terrorism%E2%80%94also%20referred%20to%20as%20global%20terrorism.%20Similar%20patterns%20of%20revival%20could%20emerge%20in%20East%20and%20West%20Africa%2C%20where%20Al%20Shabab%20and%20Boko%20Haram%20maintain%20strongholds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20point%20is%20simple%3A%20While%20the%20world's%20attention%20is%20consumed%20by%20major%20geopolitical%20concerns%E2%80%94such%20as%20European%20security%2C%20NATO's%20future%2C%20the%20displacement%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20and%20the%20resumption%20of%20US-Russia%20cooperation%E2%80%94there%20must%20be%20dedicated%20strategic%20minds%20focused%20on%20smaller%20conflicts.%20These%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20wars%E2%80%9D%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20reshape%20global%20security%20in%20ways%20far%20more%20destabilising%20than%20we%20may%20currently%20imagine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EThe%20writer%20is%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20Chancellor%20of%20the%20Central%20University%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Former%20GOC%20of%20the%20Srinagar-based%2015%20Corps.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740647880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F0a19pbic_terrorist-generic-ndtv-file_625x300_16_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnot-russia-ukraine-or-gaza-its-smaller-wars-that-are-reshaping-the-world-7806709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20world's%20attention%20is%20consumed%20by%20major%20geopolitical%20concerns%2C%20such%20as%20European%20security%2C%20NATO's%20future%2C%20Palestinians%2C%20and%20the%20resumption%20of%20US-Russia%20cooperation%2C%20there%20must%20be%20dedicated%20strategic%20minds%20focused%20on%20smaller%20conflicts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnot-russia-ukraine-or-gaza-its-smaller-wars-that-are-reshaping-the-world-7806709%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20%E2%80%9812th%20Fail%E2%80%99%20Farmer%20Created%20a%20Super%20Turmeric%20Variety%20%E2%80%94%20Now%20It%E2%80%99s%20Thriving%20in%2013%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%2C%20so%20far%2C%20shared%20the%20newly%20developed%20turmeric%20variety%20with%20some%20500%20farmers%20located%20in%20the%20villages%20spread%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Ratnagiri%2C%20Sindhudurg%2C%20and%20Raigad%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2048-year-old%20farmer%20Sachin%20Kamlakar%20Karekar%20of%20Abloli%20village%2C%2055%20km%20from%20Chiplun%2C%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Ratnagiri%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20variety%2C%20SK4%2C%20is%20a%20high-yielding%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffrom-rejections-to-earning-rs-50l-with-a-turmeric-biz%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturmeric%3C%2Fa%3E%20cultivar%20created%20by%20Karekar.%20He%20was%20among%20a%20select%20group%20of%20grassroots%20innovators%20honoured%20by%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu%20at%20the%2011th%20Biennial%20National%20Grassroots%20Innovation%20and%20Outstanding%20Traditional%20Knowledge%20Awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20local%20variety%20to%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%2030%20varieties%20grown%20in%20different%20states%2C%20SK4%20is%20the%20newest%20addition%20to%20the%20family%20of%20%3Cem%3ECurcuma%20Longa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20yellow%20spice%20we%20use%20in%20our%20food%2C%20ceremonies%2C%20and%20traditional%20Indian%20medicine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Newly%20planted%20turmeric%20saplings%20deck%20field%20in%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-300x139.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-500x231.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-768x355.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-150x69.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-410057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENewly%20planted%20turmeric%20saplings%20deck%20field%20in%20Maharashtra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sangli%E2%80%99s%20Rajapuri%20Salem%20variety%20accounts%20for%2070%25%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345836%2Fmadhya-pradesh-farmer-kanchan-verma-earns-double-income-growing-organic-turmeric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturmeric%20production%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Though%20grown%20in%20over%2020%20states%2C%20the%20largest%20share%20is%20contributed%20by%20four%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F407624%2Fkrushi-sarathi-app-for-farmers-in-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20In%202022-23%2C%20India%20produced%C2%A011.61%20lakh%20tonnes%C2%A0of%20turmeric%20making%20it%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20producer%2C%20consumer%2C%20and%20exporter.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%201998%2C%20I%20planted%20the%20local%20variety%2C%20Kadja%2C%20and%20observed%20a%20few%20plants%20that%20were%20early%20maturing%20and%20possessed%20good%20vigour.%20I%20harvested%20the%20produce%20from%20these%20plants%20and%20selected%20the%20ones%20untouched%20by%20disease%2C%20had%20bigger%20rhizomes%2C%20were%20bright%20in%20colour%20and%20high-yielding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Karekar%2C%20who%20introduces%20himself%20as%20%E2%80%9C12%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20fail%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20has%20been%20growing%20turmeric%20as%20an%20intercrop%20between%20the%20500%20areca%20nut%20palms%2C%20and%2050%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354850%2Fhomemaker-entrepreneur-organic-coconut-greenaura-oil-pickles-business-kerala-sumila-jayaraj%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut%20palms%3C%2Fa%3E%20standing%20on%20his%20family%20farm%20since%20the%20age%20of%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20call%20it%20SK-4%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202008%2C%20Karekar%20was%20able%20to%20develop%20a%20superior%20clone%20with%20all%20the%20desired%20traits%20and%20named%20it%20SK-4%2C%20taking%20the%20first%20letter%20of%20Shendge%20Kaka%2C%20the%20farmer%20who%20initially%20gave%20him%20tubers%20of%20Sangli%20Kadapa%20variety%2C%20Special%20Konkan%2C%20and%20his%20own%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202020%20Kharif%20season%2C%20the%20Dapoli-based%20Dr%20Balasaheb%20Sawant%20Konkan%20Krishi%20Vidyapeeth%20(DBSKKV)%20carried%20out%20validation%20trials%20at%20the%20National%20Innovation%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20(NIF)%20behest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnif.org.in%2Finnovation%2Fimproved-high-yielding-turmeric-variety%2F1143%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENIF%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20variety%20was%20promising%2C%20with%20a%20high%20rhizome%20yield%20(56t%2Fha).%20Among%20the%2032%20tested%20varieties%2C%20SK-4%20was%20observed%20to%20be%20superior%20over%2028%20check%20varieties%20and%20at%20par%20with%20the%20best%20check%20variety%20Sona%20(64t%2Fha)%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20yield%2Fha.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Kamlakar%20Karekar%20stands%20beside%20a%20harvest%20of%20the%20SK-4%20turmeric%20variety%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839-500x225.jpg%20500w%2