7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Critical%20Indian%20Student's%20Father%20Called%20To%20US%20For%20Her%20%26quot%3BMedical%20Decisions%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENilam%20Shinde%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20Indian%20student%20from%20Maharashtra's%20Satara%20district%2C%20is%20battling%20for%20her%20life%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20United%20States'%20California%20after%20an%20accident%20earlier%20this%20month.%20According%20to%20her%20family%2C%20there%20is%20a%20minor%20improvement%20in%20her%20health%2C%20but%20she%20remains%20in%20a%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shinde%20is%20a%20final-year%20postgraduate%20student%20at%20California%20State%20University.%20She%20met%20with%20a%20very%20serious%20accident%20on%20February%2014%2C%20while%20she%20was%20out%20on%20an%20evening%20walk.%20A%20car%20hit%20her%20from%20behind%2C%20leading%20to%20critical%20injuries%20to%20both%20her%20arms%2C%20legs%2C%20head%20and%20chest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20currently%20admitted%20in%20a%20comatose%20state%20at%20UC%20Davis%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Sacramento%2C%20California.%20However%2C%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20her%20treatment%2C%20the%20hospital%20has%20requested%20father%20come%20to%20America%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20assist%20with%20her%20medical%20care%20planning%20decisions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs%20Shinde%20is%20in%20critical%20condition%20with%20an%20uncertain%20prognosis%20and%20is%20receiving%20care%20in%20the%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20California%20State%20University%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20patient's%20father%20must%20assist%20the%20UC%20Davis%20Medical%20Center%20care%20team%20with%20making%20Ms%20Shinde's%20medical%20care%20planning%20decisions.%20Ms%20Shinde%20is%20not%20able%20to%20communicate%20due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20her%20injuries%20and%20because%20she%20is%20currently%20intubated%2C%20on%20a%20life%20support%20ven