that%20oversees%20Medicaid's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-medicaid-cuts-republicans-congress-budget-reconciliation-elon-musk-interview-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%20aims%20to%20cut%20%24880%20billion%20over%20a%20decade%20as%20part%20of%20the%20House's%20narrowly%20passed%20budget%20outline.%20The%20math%20points%20to%20those%20cuts%20including%20Medicaid%2C%20since%20it%20and%20Medicare%20%E2%80%94which%20the%20Trump%20administration%20said%20it%20would%20not%20cut%20%E2%80%94%20make%20up%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20that%20committee's%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20states%20such%20as%20New%20Mexico%2C%20California%2C%20and%20New%20York%2C%20over%20a%20third%20of%20residents%20receive%20Medicaid%2C%20per%20a%20Business%20Insider%20analysis%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medicaid.gov%2Fstate-overviews%2Fstate-profiles%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedicaid%20enrollment%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20October%202024%20and%20Census%20Bureau%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fprograms-surveys%2Fpopest.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopulation%20estimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20July%202024.%20The%20analysis%20found%20that%20about%2023.3%25%20of%20all%20Americans%20receive%20Medicaid%20or%20the%20Children's%20Health%20Insurance%20Program%2C%20which%20is%20for%20children%20in%20families%20who%20make%20too%20much%20to%20qualify%20for%20Medicaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20map%20shows%20the%20percentage%20of%20each%20state's%20residents%20who%20received%20coverage%20for%20Medicaid%20or%20CHIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FmVgOx%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Percentage%20of%20residents%20in%20each%20state%20on%20Medicaid%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22477%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAreas%20with%20higher%20percentages%20of%20Medicaid%20recipients%20included%20the%20West%2C%20Southwest%2C%20and%20Northeast%2C%20while%20parts%20of%20the%20Midwest%20and%20South%20relied%20less%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-medicaid-snap-benefits-income-reliance-increases-aging-population-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedicaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Utah%20was%20least%20reliant%20at%209.7%25%2C%20followed%20by%20Wyoming%20at%2010.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20October%2C%20Medicaid%20provides%20health%20and%20long-term%20care%20coverage%20to%20over%2072%20million%20Americans%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20predominantly%20those%20with%20low%20incomes%20and%20few%20other%20resources.%20Another%207.2%20million%20children%20under%20age%2018%20receive%20payments%20from%20CHIP.%20Medicaid%20is%20financed%20by%20federal%20and%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Speaker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmike-johnson-elon-musk-doge-government-spending-usaid-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMike%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20budget%20plan%20doesn't%20explicitly%20call%20for%20Medicaid%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20some%20Republican%20leaders%20have%20proposed%20per-capita%20caps%20on%20Medicaid%2C%20which%20would%20fix%20federal%20funding%20amounts%20per%20enrollee.%20A%20House%20Budget%20Committee%20proposal%20estimated%20this%20move%20could%20save%20up%20to%20%24900%20billion.%20Others%20have%20backed%20a%20proposal%20to%20install%20a%20Medicaid%20work%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20House%20vote%20is%20only%20the%20first%20step%20in%20a%20long%20process.%20Senate%20Republicans%20have%20competing%20plans%2C%20which%2C%20unlike%20the%20House's%20proposal%2C%20do%20not%20include%20an%20extension%20of%20Trump's%202017%20tax%20law%20or%20new%20prop