ages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20Hartz%2C%20an%20early%20Uber%20angel%20investor%2C%20directed%20his%20VC%20firm%20A%20Star%20Capital%20to%20take%20Waymos%20only.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHartz%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20believes%20Waymo%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bleast%20expensive%20option.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20investor%20at%20A%20Star%20roughly%20estimated%20spending%20about%20%2410K%20on%20Waymos%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-vc-firms-funding-creator-economy-startups-next-phase-2024-6%23a-star-has-been-investing-in-ai-powered-tools-that-help-creators-make-content-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKevin%20Hartz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20early%20Uber%20angel%20investor%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Eventbrite%2C%20directed%20his%20San%20Francisco-based%20venture%20capital%20firm%2C%20A%20Star%20Capital%2C%20to%20only%20take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaymo%20robotaxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20because%20he%20believes%20they%20provide%20the%20best%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo%20is%20now%20required%20in%20SF%20as%20it%20is%20always%20substantially%20lower%20price%20and%20often%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartz%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20his%20firm%20of%2010%20employees%20on%20January%2016%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20on%20X.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VC%20head%20wrote%20that%20a%20ride%20in%20an%20Uber%20%26quot%3BGreen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sustainable%20ride%20option%20offered%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20was%20%2450%20to%20his%20destination%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20whereas%20a%20ride%20back%20with%20a%20Waymo%2C%20which%20only%20operates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-jaguar-all-electric-self-driving-cars-i-pace-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJaguar%20I-PACE%3C%2Fa%3E%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20was%20%2419.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartz%20told%20Business%20Insider%20over%20the%20phone%20that%20his%20email%20was%20indeed%20a%20serious%20mandate%20given%20that%20employees%20get%20their%20rideshare%20costs%20comped%20by%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo%20is%20simply%20a%20better%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believes%20%26quot%3Bit's%20the%20safest%20and%20the%20fastest%20when%20you%20think%20about%20its%20ability%20to%20calculate%20the%20most%20efficient%20route.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20can%20substitute%20Waymo%20with%20another%20rideshare%20platform%20if%20wait%20times%20are%20too%20long%20and%20would%20make%20firm%20employees%20late%20to%20the%20office%2C%20Hartz%20wrote%20in%20the%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Waymo%20began%20offering%20rides%20to%20the%20SF%20public%20in%20June%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-alphabet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphabet-owned%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20chipped%20away%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxis-driverless-taxi-hurt-uber-lyft-drivers-waymo-tesla-zoox-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erideshare%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20that%20was%20once%20solely%20dominated%20by%20Uber%20and%20Lyft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-dara-khosrowshahi-helped-turn-billion-dollar-profit-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber%20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20the%20third-quarter%20earnings%20call%20in%20October%20that%20the%20company%20puts%20Waymo's%20market%20share%20within%20its%20limited%20operating%20areas%20of%20SF%20at%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20single-digits%20or%20low%20double%20digits.%26quot%3B%20He%20did%20not%20state%20an%20exact%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20it%20averages%20150%2C000%20rides%20per%20week%20throughout%20its%20operating%20cities.%20The%20robotaxi%20company%20does%20not%20offer%20rides%20on%20San%20Francisco's%20highways%20or%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Waymo%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20study%20conducted%20last%20year%20by%20Evercore%20ISI%2C%20comparing%201%2C000%20trips%20across%20the%20Waymo%2C%20Uber%2C%20and%20Lyft%20platforms%2C%20analysts%20found%20that%20Waymo's%20pricing%20has%20become%20increasingly%20competitive%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20Waymo%20ride%20for%20that%20quarter%20was%20%2421.91%2C%20compared%20to%20%2421.34%20for%20an%20UberX%20%E2%80%94%20the%20basic%20level%20of%20service%20the%20rideshare%20platform%20offers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%2422.36%20for%20a%20Lyft.%20Prices%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20exclude%20tips%20to%20drivers%2C%20Evercore%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20their%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Lyft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartz%20said%20he%20was%20an%20early%20believer%20in%20Uber%2C%20participating%20in%20the%20company's%20series%20B%20funding%20round%20in%202011%20at%20a%20%24300-million%20valuation.%20He%20declined%20to%20disclose%20a%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20experience%20in%20Waymo%20has%20made%20him%20a%20convert%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20privacy%20the%20robotaxi%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20quiet%20place%20where%20you%20can%20kind%20of%20reflect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhushi%20Suri%2C%20an%20ex-investor%20at%20A%20Star%2C%20had%20already%20embraced%20Hartz's%20Waymo-only%20directive%20long%20before%20he%20shared%20his%20January%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20February%2020%2C%20Suri%20took%20547%20rides%2C%20traveled%201%2C680%20miles%2C%20and%20spent%2010%2C005%20minutes%20inside%20a%20Waymo%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%20She%20roughly%20estimated%20spending%20%2410%2C000%20on%20Waymo%20rides%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20the%20way%20there%2C%20I%20was%20enchanted%2C%26quot%3B%20Suri%20told%20BI%20of%20her%20first%20Waymo%20ride.%20%26quot%3BBut%20on%20the%20ride%20back%2C%20I%20forgot.%20It's%20just%20so%20natural.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuri%20said%20she%20was%20a%20heavy%20Uber%20user%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bresented%20it.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20the%20privacy%20of%20a%20Waymo%20allows%20her%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20when%20she%20and%20her%20friends%20are%20going%20out%20and%20dressed%20for%20clubbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Waymo%2C%20there's%20no%20walk%20of%20shame%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20intimate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20and%20Lyft%20had%20originally%20pursued%20an%20in-house%20autonomous%20vehicle%20program%20before%20selling%20them%20off%20in%202020%20and%202021%2C%20respectively.%20Both%20rideshare%20platforms%20are%20pursuing%20partnerships%20with%20other%20autonomous%20vehicle%20companies%20to%20offer%20a%20robotaxi%20service%2C%20leveraging%20its%20existing%20user%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20plans%20to%20deepen%20its%20existing%20partnership%20with%20the%20Alphabet-owned%20company%20by%20managing%20a%20Waymo%20fleet%20in%20Austin%20and%20Atlanta%20sometime%20in%202025.%20The%20company%20already%20offers%20Waymos%20in%20Phoenix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20very%20happy%20that%20Uber%20had%20discontinued%20their%20self-driving%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartz%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20glad%20that%20they're%20partnering%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-uber-angel-investor-kevin-hartz-vc-a-star-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740646802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bf758ab8b41a9673f9142e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22