across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%2045%20days%2C%20every%20day%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20how%20lakhs%20of%20people%20from%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20country%20were%20moving%20towards%20the%20banks%20of%20Sangam.%20The%20wave%20of%20sentiments%20of%20bathing%20at%20Sangam%20kept%20on%20increasing.%20Every%20devotee%20was%20in%20the%20mood%20for%20just%20one%20thing%20--%20'Snan'%20(holy%20dip)%20at%20Sangam%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20who%20also%20took%20a%20dip%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-takes-holy-dip-at-maha-kumbh-in-prayagraj-7638100%5C%22%3ESangam%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%205%2C%20said%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20event%20has%20become%20a%20subject%20of%20new%20study%20for%20modern%20management%20professionals%2C%20including%20planning%20and%20policy%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20there%20is%20no%20comparison%20to%20such%20a%20huge%20event%20in%20the%20entire%20world%3B%20there%20is%20no%20other%20example%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world%20is%20surprised%20how%20such%20a%20large%20number%20of%20crores%20of%20people%20gathered%20on%20a%20river%20bank%20at%20the%20Triveni%20Sangam.%20These%20crores%20of%20people%20had%20neither%20received%20a%20formal%20invitation%20nor%20any%20prior%20information%20about%20the%20time%20to%20arrive.%20People%20simply%20set%20out%20for%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh...and%20were%20blessed%20by%20taking%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20holy%20Sangam%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20forget%20those%20pictures.%20I%20cannot%20forget%20those%20faces%20filled%20with%20immense%20joy%20and%20satisfaction%20after%20bathing.%20Be%20it%20women%2C%20elderly%20or%20disabled%20people%2C%20everyone%20did%20whatever%20they%20could%20to%20reach%20Sangam%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20said%2