ulation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Holeyachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGenetic%20resources%20like%20DNA%2C%20RNA%2C%20sperms%2C%20oocytes%2C%20or%20any%20other%20bodily%20tissues%20are%20valuable%20and%20can%20be%20biobanked.%20Preserved%20in%20liquid%20nitrogen%20at%C2%A0%20-196%20deg%20C%2C%20they%20can%20remain%20alive%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Vasudevan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Karthikeyan%20Vasudevan%2C%20Chief%20Scientist%20from%20LaCONES%20lab%2C%20CCMB%20conducted%20the%20training%20program%20for%20the%20officials%20%26amp%3B%20staffs%20of%20PNHZP%20%26amp%3B%20Bengal%20Safari%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-407796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Karthikeyan%20Vasudevan%2C%20Chief%20Scientist%