%20For%20red%20pandas%2C%20this%20is%2018-20%20months.%20But%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20numerous%20constraints%20impact%20this%20process%3A%20high%20mortality%20rates%20among%20the%20young%2C%20challenges%20in%20finding%20mates%2C%20potential%20food%20shortages%20after%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20predation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptive%20breeding%20programmes%20aim%20to%20mitigate%20these%20challenges%20by%20providing%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20adequate%20food%20and%20protection%20from%20predators%2C%20and%20by%20carefully%20selecting%20breeding%20pairs%20to%20maximise%20genetic%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darjeeling%20Zoo%20was%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20WAZA%20Conservation%20and%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20Awards%20in%202024%20for%20its%20red%20panda%20conservation%20efforts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-407798%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDarjeeling%20Zoo%20was%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20WAZA%20Conservation%20and%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20Awards%20in%202024%20for%20its%20red%20panda%20conservation%20efforts%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20seven%20individuals%2C%20you%20can%20bring%20its%20numbers%20up%20by%20actually%20planning%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20slowly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Vasudevan.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20these%20things%20don%E2%80%99t%20happen%20immediately.%20Sometimes%20it%20takes%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%20majestic%20Himalayas%2C%20the%20red%20panda%20is%20not%20just%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20natural%20beauty%2C%20but%20also%20a%20barometer%20of%20the%20health%20of%20its%20fragile%20ecosystems.%20As%20Dr%20Holeyachi%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ecosystem%20is%20an%20intricate%20and%20interconnected%20system%20where%20every%20species%20relies%20on%20others.%20Red%20pandas%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20within%20this%20ecosystem.%20By%20protecting%20red%20pandas%2C%20conservationists%20are%20simultaneously%20safeguarding%20their%20habitat%20and%20the%20diverse%20array%20of%20species%20that%20coexist%20within%20it.%20This%20integrated%20approach%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20long-term%20conservation%20of%20the%20entire%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Megha%20Chowdhury%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Padmaja%20Naidu%20Himalayan%20Zoological%20Park%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740400200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D407782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20its%20fiery%20red%20coat%2C%20masked%20face%2C%20and%20ringed%20tail%2C%20the%20red%20panda%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20creature%20out%20of%20a%20storybook.%20Yet%2C%20in%20the%20wilds%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20an%20ecosystem%20in%20peril.%20The%20Padmaja%20Naidu%20Himalayan%20Zoological%20Park%20has%20been%20tackling%20this%20crisis%20from%20the%20front%20through%20its%20conservation%20breeding%20programmes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kohli%E2%80%99s%20Century%20Wasn%E2%80%99t%20His%20Only%20Win%20%E2%80%94%206%20Heartwarming%20Ways%20He%E2%80%99s%20Making%20a%20Difference%20off%20the%20Field%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20did%20it%20again!%20On%2023%20February%202025%2C%20he%20played%20a%20match-winning%20knock%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20smashing%20a%20stunning%20100%20off%20111%20balls.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20another%20century%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20another%20reminder%20of%20why%20he%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20cricketers%20of%20all%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20think%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20greatness%20is%20only%20about%20cricket%2C%20think%20again.%20Off%20the%20field%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20just%20as%20remarkable%2C%20using%20his%20platform%20and%20success%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F398332%2Fgood-to-grab-food-waste-solution-sustainability-landfills-app-hyderabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egive%20back%20to%20society%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20ways%20that%20truly%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20six%20incredible%20things%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20doing%20beyond%20cricket%20%E2%80%94%20things%20that%20show%20his%20heart%20is%20just%20as%20big%20as%20his%20passion%20for%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Helping%20kids%20get%20an%20education%20and%20a%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20knows%20the%